reviewText:
Esta pelicula no deleita con buenos actores de diferentes estilos pero que se convinan para entretener y hacernos reir...
tipica pelicula revolucionaria con un toque de buen humor.
La Valentina (DVD) ~ Maria Felix. Very good movie. we received in nice condition. we enjoyed it. It was just in time for a gift.

while it is a cute movie, I didn't like the fact that the characters seemed like the voice was off with the movement of the mouth. It seemed to fake to me and I know it is a cartoon but my children are cartoon buffs as well as I am and they couldn't stand it. I've seen better.
This was a strange video.  We didn't even finish it.
My Granddaughter who is 6 loved this move.
It was a cute story, but was obviously made for another language with english dubbed in. The story was cute though.
